Detailed Description

PrefPlmnProvider is the provider to retrieve and manipulate the prefered plmns of the sim (GSM 11.11 V8.2.0 10.3.4). An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_prefplmn_provider_id

Following column ids are defined: c_mcc_id :NumberType: mobile country code c_mnc_id :NumberType: mobile network code c_access_technology_id NumberType: returns access technology. c_act_supported_id NumberType: returns a BOOLEAN value if access technology is supported.

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
